  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943630/extras/a02ffe58e03f37e720e82d83e6b66d06.avif?t=1734138250\" width=462 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Corpo Connections is a narrative-driven, backrooms-adjacent horror game where you link image IDs from photos of [REDACTED] anomalies to their descriptions. Use the altered descriptions to piece together what each image is showing.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943630/extras/f80a66ea6ebb3b0b39b7603561199c03.avif?t=1734138250\" width=462 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to learn more about your new job by discovering the secrets your new company would rather stay hidden. Uncover scrambled messages, solve ciphers and piece together what happened at [REDACTED]. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943630/extras/148efebdb6137c59edf0c5e04f2a9259.avif?t=1734138250\" width=462 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finish your daily tasks, interact with your coworkers and unlock minigames as you progress through the story. Use codes you find to return to these games time and again through The Breakroom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2943630/extras/88c7df5336937864eab80e2a438eceea.avif?t=1734138250\" width=462 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Survive or Succumb: </strong>Can you escape the horrors lurking in the office?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Shape Your Story:</strong> Make decisions that affect the world around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Cosmic Dread Awaits</strong>: discern whether the mysteries are scientific or supernatural </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock replayable minigames along the way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- [REDACTED]</p>",
